{
  "stem": "5799.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Before that, there are ruins of a Lithuanian King Gedimind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our Polish poet, Adam Michiewicz, was born in Novogrudok.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His poetry-- you see, while my education was rounded, because I knew Tennyson.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew all the writers here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I read Kipling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a must.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You didn't know anything about ours if you wouldn't have here a movie, You wouldn't know that Henryk Sienkiewicz existed-- the writer.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He wrote Mister Wolodyjowski, who had a wife, Bashka-- Basia-- Bess-- Bessie it would be in English-- who rode a horse, and wanted to be equal to men.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I wanted to go to the underground, my mother said that God has punished her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I read and I wanted to be Bashka.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Which was true.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when the Germans came, life was finished.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They came the summer of 1941.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The first ones they shot were 50 Jews on the marketplace, right across from our windows.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "First, they bombed us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they took our priest, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nobody will mention his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was a quiet hero.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my professor of history, Augustine-- there was a King Augustine who was a lover of Catherine the Great.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He descended from those-- was a lovely man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And en masse, at a mass in church, in Fara, he said to the Poles, that be careful.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The Jews go first, and we are next.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This is only the occupation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And somebody of the-- your own-- just like they did now in Poland with Popieluszko before-- they gave him out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were hung-- the priest with my professor in the middle of the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were all chased out, and we had to watch it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was a fearful time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "While our Nazarethen nuns-- true-- they were raped by the Russians when they came in.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
